60163 Tornado is a main-line steam locomotive built in Darlington, England. Coes Faen or as it is known The Clock Tower is a landmark in the Mawddach estuary, Barmouth North West Wales. It is sited on a natural projection into the estuary, some 300m to the east of Barmouth railway bridge. It is an eclectic Victorian Gothic house built of stone under a slate roof.
